				<div>
					<h3>Neon Wave</h3>
					<p>This was the first render I did in Blender. My goal was just to learn how the interface worked.
						To do this I followed along with <a href="https://youtu.be/W9eAVW4G8ws" target="_blank">this YouTube tutorial.</a>
					</p>
				</div>
				<video autoplay muted loop class="expandable">
